Package: LINEaR
Type: Package
Title: Diagnostic Tools for LINE Assumptions in Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ashini", "Shah", email = "ashinis@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Author: Ashini Shah [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Ashini Shah <ashinis@umich.edu>
Description: Provides clean summary output and diagnostic tools for checking 
    LINE assumptions (Linearity, Independence, Normality, Equal Variance) in 
    linear regression models. Includes visual diagnostics, statistical tests,
    and a summary report of validity for all four assumptions.
